" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來左冷禪適才這一招大是行險，他已修練了十餘年的「寒冰真氣」注於食指之上，拚著大耗內力，將計就計，便讓任我行吸了過去，不但讓他吸去，反而加催內力，急速注入對方穴道。"},{"pid":"7b0476311b341a49f9698c1682daf3bf0869ff6e","tid":573693,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"370ab54a0b658c53f29ec864d8f09e3d36d85c86","tid":573693,"uid":56900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"陳喬欣做既東方不敗改編得真心正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:44:43.000Z","msg":"林青霞最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aa454c86852c5d25101b791a216d6766a1cc0b","tid":573693,"uid":63152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"金庸咁多本 最鍾意真係笑傲 d人設內容真係一流"},{"pid":"dc738a0ab55204d5522fdbb6927d5da2c1ea4333","tid":573693,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527ce9064358385c7d949c438a406c4a6fc7492b","tid":573693,"uid":25771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"745711dd4e7f6b883894f089f761af0b8baa6950","tid":573693,"uid":166558,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"唯一一本睇書既金庸小說"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"文盲語障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"但我又明wo 頂佢個肺"},{"pid":"3e7ea837080a43e7ac66a21253c891c80975523c","tid":573693,"uid":129660,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86e2cde5b6d11a5dfa4eaed31c0876854abb7749","tid":573693,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"令狐沖同馮盈盈依一pair幾好! <br />\n<br />\n寫到個感覺出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"馮盈盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢做岳靈珊夠哂入型入格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c1c057b72e8a13016cc840d7e3f0be5975d4c5","tid":573693,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime